ot: Government Imports into the Confederate States</a><br>by Webster, C.L. III<br /><b>ISSUE: </B>Summer 2010<hr><br></li><li><a href='index.php?q=4583&field=ID&browse=yes&record=full&searching=yes&Submit=Search'>Faith, Valor, and Devotion: The Civil War Letters of William Porcher DuBose</a><br>by Emerson, W. Eric (ed.) and Stokes, Karen (ed.) <br /><b>ISSUE: </B>Summer 2010<hr><br></li><li><a href='index.php?q=4584&field=ID&browse=yes&record=full&searching=yes&Submit=Search'>Fitz Lee: A Military Biography of Major General Fitzhugh Lee, C.S.A. (new in paper)</a><br>by Longacre, Edward F.<br /><b>ISSUE: </B>Summer 2010<hr><br></li><li><a href='index.php?q=4585&field=ID&browse=yes&record=full&searching=yes&Submit=Search'>Getting Used to Being Shot at:  The Spence Family Civil War Letters (new in paper)</a><br>by Christ, Mark K.(ed.)<br /><b>ISSUE: </B>Summer 2010<hr><br></li><li><a href='index.php?q=4586&field=ID&browse=yes&record=full&searching=yes&Submit=Search'>Gettysburg as the Generals Remember it: Postwar Perspectives of Ten Commanders</a><br>by Broadwater, Robert P.<br /><b>ISSUE: </B>Summer 2010<hr><br></li><li><a href='index.php?q=4587&field=ID&browse=yes&record=full&searching=yes&Submit=Search'>Ghosts of Maryland</a><br>by Ricksecker, Mike<br /><b>ISSUE: </B>Summer 2010<hr><br></li><li><a href='index.php?q=4588&field=ID&browse=yes&record=full&searching=yes&Submit=Search'>“God Alone Knows Which Was Right”: The Blue and Gray Terrill Family of Virginia in the Civil War</a><br>by Armstrong, Richard L.<br /><b>ISSUE: </B>Summer 2010<hr><br></li><li><a href='index.php?q=4589&field=ID&browse=yes&record=full&searching=yes&Submit=Search'>Guide to Missouri Confederate Units, 1861-1865 (new in paper)</a><br>by McGhee, James E.<br /><b>ISSUE: </B>Summer 2010<hr><br></li><li><a href='index.php?q=4590&field=ID&browse=yes&record=full&searching=yes&Submit=Search'>Haunted Battlefields of the South</a><br>by Bush, Bryan and Freese, Thomas <br /><b>ISSUE: </B>Summer 2010<hr><b