in, Richard<br><b>Review:</b>  by <a href="index.php?q=Buman,+Nathan&field=Reviewer&browse=Yes&searching=yes&submit=Search">Buman, Nathan</a><br /><b>ISSUE: </B>Fall 2009<hr><br></li><li><a href='index.php?q=4378&field=ID&browse=yes&record=full&searching=yes&Submit=Search'>A Savage Conflict:  The Decisive Role of Guerrillas in the American Civil War</a><br>by Sutherland, Daniel E.<br><b>Review:</b>  by <a href="index.php?q=Neely,+Jeremy&field=Reviewer&browse=Yes&searching=yes&submit=Search">Neely, Jeremy</a><br /><b>ISSUE: </B>Fall 2009<hr><br></li><li><a href='index.php?q=4379&field=ID&browse=yes&record=full&searching=yes&Submit=Search'>Commanding Lincoln’s Navy: Union Naval Leadership During the Civil War</a><br>by Taaffe, Stephen R.<br><b>Review:</b>  by <a href="index.php?q=Mitchell-Cook,+Amy&field=Reviewer&browse=Yes&searching=yes&submit=Search">Mitchell-Cook, Amy</a><br /><b>ISSUE: </B>Fall 2009<hr><br></li><li><a href='index.php?q=4386&field=ID&browse=yes&record=full&searching=yes&Submit=Search'>Faces of the Confederacy:  An Album of Southern Soldiers and Their Stories</a><br>by Coddington, Ronald S.<br><b>Review:</b>  by <a href="index.php?q=Daley,+John&field=Reviewer&browse=Yes&searching=yes&submit=Search">Daley, John</a><br /><b>ISSUE: </B>Fall 2009<hr><br></li><li><a href='index.php?q=4387&field=ID&browse=yes&record=full&searching=yes&Submit=Search'>Jayhawkers: The Civil War Brigade of James Henry Lane</a><br>by Benedict, Bryce D.<br><b>Review:</b>  by <a href="index.php?q=Klunder,+Willard+Carl&field=Reviewer&browse=Yes&searching=yes&submit=Search">Klunder, Willard Carl</a><br /><b>ISSUE: </B>Fall 2009<hr><br></li><li><a href='index.php?q=4388&field=ID&browse=yes&record=full&searching=yes&Submit=Search'>Robert E. Lee and the Fall of the Confederacy, 1863-1865</a><br>by Rafuse, Ethan S.<br><b>Review:</b>  by <a href="index.php?q=Fowler,+John+D.&field=Reviewer&browse=Yes&searching=yes&submit=Search">Fowler, John D.</a><br /><b>ISSUE: </B>Fall 2009<hr><br></